Primary task:

Create a source-backed diff audit comparing the working A733 vendor kernel/source evidence with the closest upstream/mainline kernel source. Focus on the A733 SDMMC0 IDMAC descriptor-read stall and the known clue that CCU register 0x02002580 bit 27 changes behavior.

Expected output directory:

/srv/projects/homelab/task-packets/kernel/hermes-source-diff/

